com.nutiteq.packagemanager

Class PackageTileMask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nutiteq.packagemanager.PackageTileMask

  • public class PackageTileMask
extends java.lang.Object
    Tile mask contains map package spatial coverage information and
    can be used for very fast 'tile in package' tests.

        public PackageTileStatus getTileStatus(int zoom,

                                       int y)
        Deprecated. Use getTileStatus with MapTile argument instead.
        Returns the status of the specified tile. This method can be used for fast testing whether a tile is part of the package.
        Parameters:
        zoom - The zoom level of the tile.
        x - The x coordinate of the tile.
        y - The y coordinate of the tile. Note that the y-coordinate is flipped.
